# vLLM-HybridAttn (MiniCPM-SALA)

Two-PR upstream integration targeting vLLM 0.24.0 @ 8cfeb84.

- **PR1** (`vllm/model_executor/models/minicpm_sala.py`): hybrid schedule, Lightning attention, dense GQA for minicpm4 layers. **Zero sparse imports.**
- **PR2** (`pr2/` overlay): InfLLM-V2 sparse backend, KV cache spec, wiring. Never import sparse modules from PR1.

Target hardware: NVIDIA A40 (sm_86, Ampere, bf16). No FP8. page_block_size % 256 == 0 for infllm_v2.

Authoritative split: `docs/pr_split_plan.md`. Gates: `make gate-pr1`, `make gate-full`.

Treat every change as production inference code. Minimize scope; match existing vLLM conventions.